Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.21,0:00:25.78,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}絢爛奪目 不堪直視
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.17,0:00:31.10,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}初始不期而至 迅如暴風
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.28,0:00:35.98,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}被你的眸 深深吸入
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.33,0:00:41.38,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}初感的衝動 因為你的全部
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.23,0:00:46.40,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}想窺探 想知曉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.24,0:00:55.16,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}未知的你 真實的心請允許我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.30,0:00:58.23,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}數著星星的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.41,0:01:00.38,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你與我邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.42,0:01:03.56,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}兒時仰望天際
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.60,0:01:06.03,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}虔誠祈禱的我已翱翔在天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.17,0:01:08.30,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}胸中栽培夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.46,0:01:10.50,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}思念孕育力量
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.54,0:01:13.80,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}願與你攜手去往無限
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.96,0:01:17.81,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}成為導航未來之光
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.78,0:01:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,在我的提議下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.55,0:01:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Megafauna決定駛往Capital特區
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.08,0:01:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,途中雖然受到軍隊襲擊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.39,0:01:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,好在Capital衛隊出手相救
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.24,0:01:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,總算如願見到法皇大人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.94,0:01:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,但就在這時 凱爾貝斯中尉突然把我帶走
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.24,0:01:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,逃離特區
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.26,0:02:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.21,0:02:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,法皇大人 您這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.58,0:02:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,突然想到一些事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.78,0:02:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,上回與上校見面
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.94,0:02:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,還是在梅特巴爾的國際會議上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.24,0:02:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,更準確的說
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.35,0:02:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,是亞美利亞私建宇宙艦隊和機動戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.89,0:02:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,引發爭論的那場會議
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.71,0:02:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,但是當時
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.80,0:02:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,月球背後 發現名為托瓦薩格的殖民衛星
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.13,0:02:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,已經成為無法迴避的事實！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.96,0:02:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,眼看禁忌失去管束力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.04,0:02:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你便想挾持法皇為人質
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.21,0:02:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,搭乘海盜船登上聖波爾圖 我沒說錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.17,0:02:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,真佩服您的想像力！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.75,0:02:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,起碼在我看來…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.04,0:03:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.31,0:03:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,所謂艦隊 到底是真是假？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.35,0:03:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,好一個熱鬧的週末
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.26,0:03:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,茹甘司令有請
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.28,0:03:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,去諾蕾朵家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.86,0:03:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,他們好像沒這個打算
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.03,0:03:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.22,0:03:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,軍隊不僅對Megafauna和G-Self垂涎三尺
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.21,0:03:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,好像連那女孩也不願放過
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.45,0:03:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.55,0:03:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,他們認為她知道宇宙來的威脅吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.13,0:03:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,誰讓她是從天上掉下來的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.90,0:03:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,別驚動軍隊 盡可能低空飛行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.19,0:03:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,這您放心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.62,0:03:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,別怕 姐姐在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.71,0:04:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,如諸位所見
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.81,0:04:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,這架Ousia只是開發計劃的冰山一角
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.43,0:04:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,待後續機型陸續投產
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.72,0:04:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,還須仰仗各位議員
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.99,0:04:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,一如既往的理解與支持…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.08,0:04:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我還沒…！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.49,0:04:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,首相閣下所言極是！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.38,0:04:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,不論面對任何事態
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.08,0:04:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Capital軍都必須能夠第一時間作出回應！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.34,0:04:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,精彩的訓話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.87,0:04:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.45,0:04:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,要議會繼續通過預算案
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.23,0:04:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,就必須多打勝仗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.71,0:04:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.03,0:04:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,已經在安排宇宙戰艦 請您放心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.93,0:04:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,辛苦上校了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.84,0:04:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我看中的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.56,0:04:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,那邊的！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.18,0:04:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.29,0:04:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,那架新型機動戰士的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.81,0:04:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Ousia 好像很早以前的鎧甲騎士
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.70,0:04:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 是啊是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.63,0:04:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,誒 還真能裝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.59,0:05:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,向中尉的付出表示感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.83,0:05:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,區區小事 何必行此大禮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.34,0:05:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,原來她會感謝人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.61,0:05:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,長官…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.49,0:05:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,長官的事也必須感謝你們
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.41,0:05:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,宇宙工作的衛隊成員親口向我保證
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.15,0:05:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,這艘Megafauna能夠順利上天
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.80,0:05:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.51,0:05:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,可是 Capital軍已經知道了我們的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.01,0:05:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,關於宇宙的威脅 好像真有其事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.53,0:05:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,臍帶教法皇說的？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.34,0:05:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,去諾蕾朵家…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.99,0:05:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,不對不對
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.19,0:05:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,不對不對
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.96,0:05:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,請艾達小姐負責Megafauna的護衛工作
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.42,0:05:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是個替補的駕駛員嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.50,0:05:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,總監大人看著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.72,0:05:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,現在他不在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.44,0:05:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,已經交給長官了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.15,0:05:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,交給長官？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.78,0:05:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,就是貝魯利的媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.63,0:06:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,全員 準備升空
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.64,0:06:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.66,0:06:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Arcane是我的座機
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.19,0:06:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,該裝的武器一樣不許少！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.70,0:06:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,果然是突擊娘啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.90,0:06:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,誒？G-Self哪裏去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.01,0:06:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,這不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.76,0:06:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,還要一會兒 你先去準備
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.19,0:06:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,話是這麼說 可上不了G-Self
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.50,0:06:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我準備什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.43,0:06:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,這是從Capital軍那裏拿來的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.16,0:06:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼是從Capital軍拿來的？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.24,0:06:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,當然是這台陸戰用高機動背包
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.90,0:06:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.78,0:06:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,看到G-Self和這台背包
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.47,0:06:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,漸漸明白玫瑰設計圖和G系列的關係
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.55,0:06:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,忍不住想裝上試試
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.52,0:06:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,建造Ousia時同期造的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.28,0:06:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,事後才發現Ousia裝不上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.52,0:06:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.51,0:06:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我猜是給這東西用的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.61,0:06:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你用過不少背包了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.75,0:06:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,這可不是遊戲 教官
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.39,0:07:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,不許再喊教官
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.93,0:07:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,是戰友 明白麼戰友！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.32,0:07:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以向總統進言
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.17,0:07:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,下令宇宙艦隊暫緩出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.00,0:07:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,這裏距離Capital塔的底部站點
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.44,0:07:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,只有一小時多點的路程
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.41,0:07:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,從站點駕駛大氣層滑翔機
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.95,0:07:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,轉眼 便可飛回祖國
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.25,0:07:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,能借我一用嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.83,0:07:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,因為近乎觸犯禁忌
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.88,0:07:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,非常昂貴哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.22,0:07:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,香草的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.63,0:07:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜歡這香味
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.02,0:07:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,這也是迫不得已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.95,0:07:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,全當為了Capital塔的安全
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.00,0:07:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,相當不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.63,0:07:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.29,0:07:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我會坐今天的末班車
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.63,0:07:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,前往聖波爾圖
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.80,0:07:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,您確定嗎 得耗時整整一周
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.30,0:07:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,每年不都這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.64,0:07:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼 二位一起？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.40,0:07:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 麻煩告知Megafauna
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.51,0:07:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,這裏有電話 由我來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.59,0:08:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,果然好喝！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.74,0:08:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,說是Capital軍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.61,0:08:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,跟菜鳥沒什麼分別
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.00,0:08:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,但也不能掉以輕心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.02,0:08:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,明白 公主殿下！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.83,0:08:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我也…不是萬能的呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.57,0:08:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,找回當衛隊時的心態
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.39,0:08:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs45}啊啊啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.52,0:08:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 站住！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.71,0:08:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.27,0:08:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,讓他們去睡覺！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.11,0:08:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,拉萊雅
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.13,0:08:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,出動 G-Self出動！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.67,0:08:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,真會給人添亂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.28,0:08:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,那孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.94,0:08:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,貝魯利也是 搞什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.57,0:08:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,看 啾啾咪說去睡覺
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.11,0:08:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,睡不著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.45,0:08:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,她突然大喊大叫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.43,0:08:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,她剛才說G-Self？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.34,0:08:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.11,0:09:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,G-Self交給貝魯利就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.06,0:09:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.23,0:09:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,拉萊雅她…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.82,0:09:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.58,0:09:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,G-Self怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.36,0:09:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,去問中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.14,0:09:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,那孩子 感覺變了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.21,0:09:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,來了 來了 來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.78,0:09:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Capital衛隊的？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.35,0:09:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,機動戰士進入迎擊狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.15,0:09:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Capital衛隊的Recksnow前來會合
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.61,0:09:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,有佩戴頭巾 別認錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.79,0:09:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,凱爾貝斯中尉也來保護這艘船嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.98,0:09:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,不光是奉命行事哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.49,0:09:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,這艘Megafauna很讓人著迷 嘿嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.20,0:09:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 是軍艦迷？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.60,0:09:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,看不起軍迷？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.75,0:09:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,哪裏 求之不得
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.88,0:09:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,實在感謝您 長官
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.02,0:09:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,好 有線電話就此掛斷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.06,0:10:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,回頭見
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.25,0:10:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,G-Self什麼情況？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.15,0:10:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Capital軍的G系背包不好調試…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.94,0:10:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,能用就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.77,0:10:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.61,0:10:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,貝魯利在幹嘛？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.29,0:10:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,在傷心欲絕 因為失去存在意義！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.85,0:10:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,貝克部隊的Ousia
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.83,0:10:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,為剿滅宇宙海盜 在此發誓…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.68,0:10:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,蠢貨！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.07,0:10:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,要活捉G-Self
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.30,0:10:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,拉萊雅·曼蒂 貝魯利·賽納姆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.86,0:10:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,確保他們的安全才是本次作戰的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.82,0:10:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Catsith部隊 好好給Ousia提供掩護！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.36,0:10:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,噢！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.09,0:10:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼 讓他們瞧瞧Ousia的精確打擊能力！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.33,0:10:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,噢噢！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.16,0:10:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,太帥了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.32,0:10:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,男人的世界啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.79,0:10:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,加油加油 Ousia
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.86,0:11:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,幹掉宇宙海盜船！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.78,0:11:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,這些女人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.18,0:11:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 是我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.71,0:11:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,能聯繫到面具嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.31,0:11:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 這就來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.12,0:11:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,這裏是Capital塔腳下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.90,0:11:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,不許主動開火
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.67,0:11:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Catsith和雙體踏板
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.28,0:11:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,力求分割Megafauna和機動兵力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.21,0:11:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,海盜船上為什麼有Recksnow？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.02,0:12:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,公主殿下說了 不放心Capital衛隊的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.24,0:12:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,這個倔頭倔腦的野丫頭！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.78,0:12:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ousia部隊攻取Megafauna
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.59,0:12:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Catsith是航空部隊的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.69,0:12:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我們則擁有宇宙部隊的輕盈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.52,0:12:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,只須輕輕一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.65,0:12:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,艦…艦橋在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.35,0:12:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,G-Self …不是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.20,0:12:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Capital軍竟然出動這麼多地面部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.52,0:12:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,到底怎麼想的？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.60,0:12:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,那確實是G系機體
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.28,0:12:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,貝魯利和拉萊雅在船上什麼地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.57,0:12:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,去恐嚇艦橋 逼他們從船裏出來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.77,0:13:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,海盜船船長 聽得見吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.20,0:13:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,將G-Self和貝魯利·賽納姆
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.31,0:13:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,以及拉萊雅·曼蒂交給我方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.20,0:13:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,命令機體停止抵抗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.70,0:13:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,自己撒的米諾夫斯基粒子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.93,0:13:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你倒是給個聯繫的辦法！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.26,0:13:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,要人自己去抓
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.72,0:13:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼…啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.51,0:13:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你小子算什麼意思！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.03,0:13:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,人家在一本正經交涉…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.72,0:13:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,滾一邊去！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.28,0:13:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,他們連拉萊雅也要 到底怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.73,0:13:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,鬼知道 反正Capital的人盯上她了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.52,0:13:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,留個心眼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.75,0:13:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.92,0:13:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,別亂跑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.81,0:13:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,會被打出洞洞眼的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.31,0:13:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,光束武器的…戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.21,0:13:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,給她穿上太空服
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.12,0:13:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,給她…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.06,0:13:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,太空服！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.29,0:14:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,那不是Ousia嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.57,0:14:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,軍隊又偷偷摸摸搞些實戰兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.47,0:14:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Megafauna危險！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.10,0:14:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,又來一架
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.46,0:14:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你們有什麼企圖？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.32,0:14:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,交出貝魯利和拉萊雅…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.40,0:14:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,這是命令！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.16,0:14:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.28,0:14:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.85,0:14:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,那是 艾達小姐的腿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.65,0:14:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,哈朋先生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.75,0:14:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,不管背包多強力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.88,0:14:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,用不了也沒意義！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.68,0:14:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,這種話不用你跟我說
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.63,0:14:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,飛出去守不住Megafauna的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.41,0:14:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我們所有人都得死
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.10,0:14:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,艾達小姐 別勉強啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.67,0:14:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,動心了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.92,0:14:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,不是這種問題！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.48,0:14:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,這機體和G-Self有幾分相似
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.95,0:15:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我們來彼此瞭解下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.74,0:15:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,哈朋先生！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.33,0:15:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,功率上來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.15,0:15:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.04,0:15:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.12,0:15:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,別急急忙忙衝出去掛了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.10,0:15:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,才戀愛 換你肯死嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.85,0:15:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,著地前打開氣墊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.27,0:15:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,艾達小姐在哪裏？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.67,0:16:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,有兩下子 我喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.95,0:16:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Capital軍開發的Ousia
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.00,0:16:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我愛上這鐵疙瘩了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.69,0:16:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,機體馬力…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.06,0:16:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.53,0:16:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.12,0:16:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,還有你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.94,0:16:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,那應該不會爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.26,0:16:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,艾達小姐在哪裏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.90,0:16:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.60,0:16:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,艾達小姐被…抓住了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.42,0:16:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼東西鑽進叢林了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.10,0:17:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,力量完敗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.08,0:17:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都在各自為戰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.39,0:17:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,只有自己來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.06,0:17:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,也太瞧不起人了吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.85,0:17:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.82,0:17:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,飛吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.00,0:18:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,是貝魯利一個人的主意？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.32,0:18:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,為…為了艾達小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.35,0:18:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Capital軍？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.40,0:18:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,前面就是Capital塔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.95,0:18:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,回去吧 別幹傻事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.23,0:18:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,要…要沉了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.03,0:18:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,要沉了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.08,0:18:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,來人！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.77,0:18:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,別靠近！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.89,0:18:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,別過來 離遠點救我！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.93,0:18:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,還真是 竟然沒有陷入沼澤
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.16,0:18:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,腿部傳感器的性能很棒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.73,0:18:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,能知道腳下地面的軟硬程度
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.51,0:18:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,小心加速度
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.90,0:18:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,尾翼壞了 我有心理準備
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.52,0:18:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼 我們回Megafauna號
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.99,0:19:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Megafauna號上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.42,0:19:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,新加入了Capital衛隊的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.07,0:19:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 Capital軍的做法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.35,0:19:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,讓很多人反感吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.73,0:19:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽也一定會同意我回那裏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.24,0:19:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,G-Self和Arcane返航
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.96,0:19:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,應該是前甲板吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.62,0:19:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.08,0:19:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,糟糕 盧安先生惱火了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.82,0:19:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,貝魯 把她們收容進來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.33,0:19:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,拉萊雅在甲板上幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.53,0:20:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,拉萊雅·曼蒂…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.13,0:20:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,多虧這台背包 撿回了性命…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.37,0:20:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,這種東西 存在 真的好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.59,0:20:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,法皇大人說威脅並不來自宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.21,0:20:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,而是來自地球人 這話發人深思
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.70,0:20:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.32,0:20:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,冠艇的發車時間快到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.83,0:20:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,先告辭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.07,0:20:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,全權負責將總監安全送到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.48,0:20:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.51,0:20:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.20,0:20:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,關於亞美利亞國家電視台的新聞…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.11,0:20:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,國家電視台？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.89,0:20:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,總統命令宇宙艦隊出擊？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.11,0:20:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,您何時上船的？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.14,0:21:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,來得匆忙 所以乘了最後一節貨車
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.52,0:21:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,調查部的上校來此有何貴幹？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.04,0:21:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,是我從貢德梵借來Garanden號
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.80,0:21:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,必須對它的一舉一動負責
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.45,0:21:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,難得您一番苦心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.02,0:21:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,按預定時間發車
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.10,0:21:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我在這裏稍作休息
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.17,0:21:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,是 請好好休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.90,0:21:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,MMF正常啟動 發車
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.35,0:21:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,容易漏氣的地方全部塞上填充物
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.80,0:21:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,人做不到的由機動戰士完成
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.74,0:22:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,好 星艦Garanden號
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.05,0:22:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,進入環地軌道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.75,0:22:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,與面具上尉會合後
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.82,0:22:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,前往阻止亞美利亞軍攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.83,0:24:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,自從乘上Megafauna
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.70,0:24:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,對外界發生的事一無所知
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.59,0:24:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,來到衛星軌道的我
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.00,0:24:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,被人偶一樣的機動戰士襲擊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.72,0:24:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,被迫進行肉搏
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.88,0:24:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,還險些丟了性命
